# graphrag Directory Guide

The [graphrag/](mdc:graphrag) directory contains logic for graph-based retrieval and entity resolution, including:

- [search.py](mdc:graphrag/search.py): Graph-based search logic.
- [utils.py](mdc:graphrag/utils.py): Utility functions for graph-based retrieval.
- [entity_resolution.py](mdc:graphrag/entity_resolution.py): Entity resolution logic.
- [entity_resolution_prompt.py](mdc:graphrag/entity_resolution_prompt.py): Prompt templates for entity resolution.
- [query_analyze_prompt.py](mdc:graphrag/query_analyze_prompt.py): Query analysis prompt logic.
- [general/](mdc:graphrag/general): General graph-based logic.
- [light/](mdc:graphrag/light): Lightweight graph-based logic.

See each referenced file or subdirectory for more details on graph-based retrieval and entity resolution.
